short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Modify YouTube thumbnails to make them more degenerate.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
In layman's terms this extension makes every video you see look similar to a Turkey Tom one.

Notes: 
- This extension was inspired by MrBeastify: 
https://github.com/MagicJinn/MrBeastify-Youtube
- This extension is made purely for fun and is for obvious comedic purposes.
- This extension is unofficial and not affiliated with Turkey Tom or YouTube.

Source: https://github.com/Nomok/Turkey-Tomify-YouTube
